N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 469.2 - Definition

State Regulations

As used in this Part, retired members shall mean a storm
member of the State Police who entered service retirement under Retirement and

Social Security Law, section
381-b after December 30, 1998. Notes
